cdata.name: Crystal Clear Token
cdata.desc:
Crystal Clear Services is a blockchain-based payment platform. It provides a set of tools for the customers and service providers to connect, negotiate, and execute paid services through services marketplace of Crystal Clear Services. The platform uses a service auction mechanism that randomly chooses 5 service providers in order to bring fairness to all participants.
The Crystal Clear Token (CCT) is an Ethereum-based (ERC-20) cryptocurrency. It is the token that fuels the platform as it is used to pay for the services available in the system as well as to stake an offer for a pretended service in an auction.
